{"tid":2282974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林建岳孻仔遇襲案 其中一名被告表證不成立 當庭釋放","createTime":"2020-11-12T08:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:04:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"824122ae96f8e4b12058c71b16e605eb98dd8e60","tid":2282974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:39:23.000Z","msg":"去年萬聖節，林建岳孻仔林孝能到蘭桂坊消遣，其間與人爭執，疑遭入境處職員「爆樽」，案件今日續審。當日與林孝能同行的友人原本被控普通襲擊，早前獲撤控並簽保守行為了事，他今出庭作供，稱林孝能當日曾謂「我屋企同我自己都係支持警察嘅」，被告聞言即指罵二人是「死藍絲」，友人及後遭次被告以金屬硬物打面。友人又稱當時林只是手持紙製槍，辯方盤問指出，林昨供稱是玩具槍，友人卻堅持只是槍狀物，更焦急謂「所以係喺我個角度嚟睇，我冇掂過支嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n林的友人何兆霖今供稱，當日首被告舉起職員證時，林曾宣稱「我屋企同我自己都係支持警察嘅」，兩被告聞言即指罵林是「死藍絲」。眾人推撞期間，次被告從褲袋取出一個物件戴上手指，並握拳向他揮擊。何登時左眼角受傷流血，並稱物件感覺是「金屬硬物」。<br />\n<br />\n何又稱當日林手持一個紙卡製槍狀物，是酒吧贈送的萬聖節道具。辯方外籍資深大狀李定國盤問時反駁指，林昨供稱手持的是「玩具膠槍」。何聞言焦急謂「所以係喺我嗰角度嚟睇，我冇掂過支野。」何再解釋「大眾角度嚟睇，真係可以射到嘢出嚟先係玩具槍。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/ZNTDVTI4GFC5VELHKMKIQ66JUA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FZNTDVTI4GFC5VELHKMKIQ66JUA%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=3e6ccb73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FZNTDVTI4GFC5VELHKMKIQ66JUA%2F&h=f992bd97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/ZNTDVTI4GFC5VELHKMKIQ66JUA/</a>"},{"pid":"831abbf694170b32d64629108cf84399e2434ddc","tid":2282974,"uid":28031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"呢單野一單野就包含左藍既撒控 黃既死咬兩大律政屍金科玉律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f7725ffe49b2e7ee65636e86f1a21ddf8e0df2","tid":2282974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"831abbf694170b32d64629108cf84399e2434ddc","tid":2282974,"uid":28031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"呢單野一單野就包含左藍既撒控 黃既死咬兩大律政屍金科玉律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965f2a06eb66f212a12d32e6b5ffda4eec0af717","tid":2282974,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"林孝撚"},{"pid":"652a7d42a2de926bf8feb87d75543b1e4245b2a5","tid":2282974,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}